*this command run web(have to be in web folder)
mvn clean install tomcat7:run

*this command run client(have to be in client folder)
mvn exec:java

*****************************************************
*Client samples

entities : activity | user 
commands : create | get | delete | list
client commands: info | exit 

Example: activity create | user list

*Client example work
Enter your command: user create
Enter user first name: Adam
Enter user last name: Brauner
Enter birthdate in dd-M-yyyy format: 10-11-1988
Enter user weight: 90
Enter user gender (male=1 / female=2): 1
Created user{id= 1 ,name= Adam Brauner ,birthday= Thu Nov 10 00:00:00 CET 1988 ,weight= 90 ,gender= MALE